import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import Header from '../Header/Header'
import Categorie from '../../components/Categories/categorie'
import ListCard from '../../components/Card/listCard'
import MiniListCard from '../../components/OftenOrder/ListMiniCard'
import Footer from '../Footer/Footer'

function MainPage() {
    const [search, setSearch] = React.useState('')

    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
                <Route path='' element={<Header search={search} setSearch={setSearch} />}/>
                <Route path='' element={<Categorie />} />
                <Route path='' element={<MiniListCard /> } /> 
                <Route path='' element={<ListCard search={search} />} />
                <Route path='' element={<Footer />} />
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default MainPage
